---
import PageLayout from '@layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Heel Mules Guide"
  description="Understanding heeled mule styles: from classic pumps to contemporary designs, construction techniques, and fashion positioning."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Encyclopedia', url: '/encyclopedia/' },
    { name: 'Categories', url: '/encyclopedia/categories/' },
    { name: 'Mules', url: '/encyclopedia/mules/' },
    { name: 'Heel Mules', url: '/encyclopedia/mules/heel-mules/' },
  ]}
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="badge-primary mb-2">Style Guide</span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Heel Mules Guide
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
      Understanding heeled mule styles: from classic pumps to contemporary designs, construction techniques, and fashion positioning.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop"
      alt="Heel Mules"
      class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h2>The Elegant Backless Heel</h2>
    
    <p>
      Heel mules combine the effortless style of the mule silhouette with the height and elegance of elevated footwear. This versatile category spans diverse heel heights and styles, from practical kitten heels to dramatic stilettos, all sharing the defining characteristic of exposed heels.
    </p>

    <h2>Heel Types</h2>
    
    <h3>Block Heels</h3>
    <p>
      Block heels provide stability and comfort while adding significant height. The wider heel surface distributes weight more evenly than stilettos.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Stability:</strong> Wider base provides better balance and reduced ankle fatigue.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Comfort:</strong> Better weight distribution enables extended wear.
    </p>

    <h3>Stiletto Mules</h3>
    <p>
      High heels create dramatic elegance, favored for evening and special occasions. The slender heel creates a sleeker silhouette.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Silhouette Enhancement:</strong> Elongates the leg and creates elegant posture.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Fashion Impact:</strong> High fashion positioning for special occasions.
    </p>

    <h3>Kitten Heels</h3>
    <p>
      Low heels offer subtle elevation with maximum comfort for everyday wear. The modest height makes kitten heels practical for professional environments.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Office Appropriate:</strong> Professional height suitable for business environments.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Extended Wear:</strong> Comfortable enough for all-day use.
    </p>

    <h2>Construction Techniques</h2>
    
    <h3>Heel Attachment</h3>
    <p>
      Heel construction in mules requires specialized approaches due to the absence of heel enclosure.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Structural Requirements:</strong> The sole must provide secure heel attachment without conventional heel seat structure.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Reinforcement:</strong> Strategic reinforcement maintains heel shape and provides adequate support.
    </p>

    <h3>Counter-Free Design</h3>
    <p>
      Mules lack the internal heel counter found in traditional shoes, requiring alternative structural solutions.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Padding Strategy:</strong> Interior cushioning compensates for reduced structural support.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Fit Design:</strong> Opening design must ensure secure fit without heel enclosure.
    </p>

    <h2>Fashion Positioning</h2>
    
    <h3>Evening Wear</h3>
    <p>
      Heel mules excel in evening and formal contexts where elegance takes priority.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Designer Focus:</strong> Major luxury brands invest heavily in mule collections.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Material Drama:</strong> Satin, metallic, and embellished options create evening impact.
    </p>

    <h3>Daytime Versatility</h3>
    <p>
      Contemporary heel mules successfully bridge casual and professional contexts.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Office Appropriate:</strong> Kitten heel mules work in professional environments.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Smart Casual:</strong> Block heel mules pair with weekend and casual professional attire.
    </p>

    <h2>China Manufacturing</h2>
    
    <h3>Quality Considerations</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Heel Security:</strong> Verify heel attachment methods and test for adequate security.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Padding Quality:</strong> Interior cushioning quality significantly impacts comfort.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Construction Standards:</strong> Confirm factory expertise with heeled construction.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
